{"tid":418405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"on9學校on9校規，禁止同學以零食代替午飯","createTime":"2017-09-29T13:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T14:57:58.000Z","uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"346f57e8de76f3c0097fd9c9bcdb106e4062ac28","tid":418405,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TeacherVoice/posts/1465153883568829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTeacherVoice%2Fposts%2F1465153883568829&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=1451b699\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TeacherVoice/posts/1465153883568829</a><br />\n老師心聲<br />\n21 小時 &middot; <br />\n#1709982<br />\n&quot;訓導工作應該係whole school approach全校參與的<br />\n上星期某日留校午膳時<br />\n門外對講機傳來領袖生對訓導主任的呼喚<br />\n但訓導主任外出午膳，人不在<br />\n學生從教員室門上玻璃見到我<br />\n於是呼召我出去<br />\n唯有丟下吃了一小半的飯盒<br />\n原來事情緊急<br />\n連我這個非訓導老師也被要求拔刀相助<br />\n有個六呎高的學生為了紀律問題<br />\n正在毆打一個小個子領袖生<br />\n我衝落去時已有兩名女同事拉開兩人<br />\n我唯有拉開大個子<br />\n其他兩位女同事也很醒目<br />\n立馬照料受傷同學的傷勢<br />\n大個子很激動<br />\n不能剛克，唯有柔克<br />\n先要求他深呼吸十數下，平伏情緒<br />\n再著他入洗手間洗臉，冷靜下來<br />\n最後先讓他吃了飯再說<br />\n十分鐘後召他出課室<br />\n單對單man's talk<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原來領袖生按訓導主任指示<br />\n不止一次阻止同學以零食代替午飯<br />\n同學當然抵賴沒有聽到相關訓示<br />\n於是以老師身份作證聽過這新規定<br />\n並一再重申，更要求學生確認收到訊息</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同學當然認錯<br />\n接著問為何出手打人<br />\n「一時衝動出了手<br />\n便索性唔收手係咁打囉<br />\n打一鎚是罰打十鎚也是罰」<br />\n唯有告訴他這樣下去只會小事化大<br />\n泥足越踩越深，最後不能自拔<br />\n正好領袖生及時出現(事前我和他商量好)<br />\n在我搭著犯事同學膊頭下<br />\n領袖生解釋了自己的執法立場<br />\n並承認語氣和態度有改善空間<br />\n最後雙方互相道歉<br />\n在我要求下握了手<br />\n協議記了個缺點(本來應該是小過或大過)<br />\n我想說如果那次代堂老師第一時間阻止學生玩魚蝦蟹<br />\n要受罰同學的數目會減少<br />\n如果這次非訓導老師硬說「我唔係訓導老師，同學打交唔關我事」<br />\n那可能最終要召喚救傷車和報警<br />\n有人要瞓醫院<br />\n有人恨錯難翻<br />\n所以訓導工作個個老師有責<br />\n「不是訓導老師」只是推卸責任的藉口&quot;<br />\n---<br />\n留言: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1LdnAkC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1LdnAkC&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=669077bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1LdnAkC</a><br />\nSTEM 服務: <a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/yc465j6r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fyc465j6r&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=55f1294a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/yc465j6r</a><br />\n培養學生抗逆能力: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pqKjCJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pqKjCJ&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=7bef5567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pqKjCJ</a>"},{"pid":"08922854cfb7b0e688607abf1a140f8f5258aaf0","tid":418405,"uid":66260,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"訓導 = 香港政府<br />\n領袖生= 黑警<br />\non9校規 = 惡法<br />\n打鳩prefect = 以武抗暴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6258d578d5dde94d630856064e913e1868cd91c7","tid":418405,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"Colin Lai 雖然重點不在此，但無理法例強制執行，市民自由受壓無法申訴被逼訴諸暴力，在香港不是很好的寫照嗎？（利申：我無話個大個子做得啱）<br />\n讚好 &middot; 回覆 &middot; 1 &middot; 14小時"},{"pid":"6df66e8afcca13fa70a6a544c63e8a308a9b9c84","tid":418405,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b56b039980a16ef4cd6b8128ac36dae0e6524b9","tid":418405,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得係德政。以前有個同學唔食飯幾年儲錢買玩具，幾年後開始胃痛，一痛十幾年了。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友係要啲 guidance, 如果唔係好易因小失大。"},{"pid":"c5f82348a56c9fdd463c03abeb6a4b9bc2edd2a2","tid":418405,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓導 = 香港政府<br />\n領袖生= 黑警<br />\non9校規 = 惡法<br />\n打鳩prefect = 以武抗暴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打柒佢！"},{"pid":"286ad180d4fe3194167fb84f60b1487ff0429eb7","tid":418405,"uid":140532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">打一鎚是罰打十鎚也是罰</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c31a7f8af6cd0f1aeae78fec6c7399e79b7990","tid":418405,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"啲口賤prefect根本就抵俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8449da9a21a6754c50297a8da015fe99e4914dc","tid":418405,"uid":101550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲口賤prefect根本就抵俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學果陣冷衫衫身唔可以長過皮帶以下16cm<br />\n衫䄂唔可以長到掂到虎口<br />\n當然 如果長到條身裙咁梗係抵死<br />\n但我16.2cm都要捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長左0.2cm有咁影響校譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n皮帶一定要黑色細扣果隻 <br />\n<br />\n唔可以摺衫袖 <br />\n<br />\n一定要扣頸喉鈕<br />\n<br />\n女仔可以帶con男同學唔可以<br />\n(有男仔面生濕疹帶眼鏡括到會痕都唔俾帶con要痕住上堂)<br />\n<br />\n男同學頭髮唔可以標奇立異  兩邊唔俾'產'<br />\n有部份老師唔俾斜陰 有部份老師唔俾平陰<br />\n唔準剪鮑魚刷頭<br />\n<br />\n結果係班prefect日尻日攞間尺捉人冷衫長 走去睇人有冇con<br />\n扯開人條呔睇人有冇扣鈕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af51ffbb0a12d0a7baa3a02258215bbae9786eca","tid":418405,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得係德政。以前有個同學唔食飯幾年儲錢買玩具，幾年後開始胃痛，一痛十幾年了。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友係要啲 guidance, 如果唔係好易因小失大。</blockquote><br />\n咁強制留校食飯呢？除左收左飯盒商油水，仲有咩作用？"}]}